OL,3,CHomes evacuated after residents report
OL,4,Csmelling gas
OL,6,FA number of people have been evacuated
OL,7,Ffrom a block of flats in Jersey after
OL,8,Fresidents reported smelling gas.
OL,10,FEmergency services and the gas company
OL,11,FIsland Energy were called to Cherry
OL,12,FOrchard Court on Valley Road in St
OL,13,FHelier on Wednesday morning (1 July).
OL,15,FA police cordon has been put in place
OL,16,Fand people are being asked to avoid
OL,17,Fthe area while investigations continue
OL,18,F- displaced residents have been
OL,19,Fevacuated to St Saviour's Parish Hall.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/4
