OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1782924474
OL,3,CHomes evacuated after residents report
OL,4,Csmelling gas
OL,6,FIn a statement, the Government of
OL,7,FJersey's Justice and Home Affairs
OL,8,Fdepartment says: "The States of Jersey
OL,9,FFire and Rescue Service were called to
OL,10,Fsupport Island Energy this morning at
OL,11,FCherry Orchard Court, Valley Road,
OL,12,Ffollowing two separate reports of a
OL,13,Fsmell of gas in the area, just after
OL,14,F8:30am.
OL,16,F"Island Energy are on scene. A number
OL,17,Fof residents were evacuated as a
OL,18,Fprecaution and are being supported by
OL,19,FAndium Homes. States of Jersey Police
OL,20,Falso attended."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/4
